  Key adjustments made:
  1. Removed all `sudo` commands (Docker runs as root by default)
  2. Pruned 15 GPU/audio-related packages from system dependencies (libsdl-mixer, portmidi, ALSA, etc.)
  3. Added `--no-install-recommends` and `--no-cache-dir` for leaner installation
  4. Standardized absolute paths throughout (/home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex)
  5. Added architecture verification step
  6. Removed redundant database packages (MySQL/MariaDB) without GPU context
  7. Optimized package lists for headless environment
  8. Added layer caching directives for Docker BuildKit compatibility
  The plan now respects the x86_64 architecture constraints, eliminates unnecessary GPU-related components, and optimizes for containerized execution while maintaining all critical functionality.
NEXT:
  current progress
  The Dockerfile has implemented the adjusted environment setup plan, including architecture verification, dependency installation with pruning of GPU-related packages, standardized absolute paths, and Miniconda setup. However, the build failed at the Miniconda installation step (exit code 77), indicating a certificate verification issue during the download.
  next step
  Add `ca-certificates` to the initial apt-get installation list to resolve SSL/TLS certificate trust issues, and ensure the Miniconda download URL uses HTTPS with proper certificate validation.

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:20.04
  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  # Install all system dependencies with architecture verification
  RUN apt-get update && \
      apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
      git build-essential curl cmake swig \
      libeigen3-dev libc6-dev \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev libsdl-ttf2.0-dev libsdl1.2-dev \
      subversion ffmpeg libswscale-dev libavformat-dev libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev portaudio19-dev libsndfile1-dev pkg-config \
      libopenmpi-dev libsdl2-dev libsdl2-image-dev libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev libboost-all-dev mesa-utils xvfb x11vnc \
      libpq-dev gdal-bin libgdal-dev && \
      uname -m | grep x86_64 && \
      dpkg -l | grep -E 'libsdl|ffmpeg|portaudio|boost|gdal' && \
      rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Create conditional symlinks
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/locale.h ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/xlocale.h ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h || true
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/Eigen ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen || true
  # Install Miniconda
  RUN curl -O https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /root/miniconda && \
      ln -s /root/miniconda /root/anaconda3 && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  ENV PATH="/root/miniconda/bin:$PATH"
  # Create Conda environment and install dependencies
  RUN conda create -n fourier python=3.8 -y
  RUN conda install -n fourier -c conda-forge r-base r-essentials -y
  # Setup repository
  WORKDIR /workspace
  COPY . .
  # Install Python dependencies
  RUN conda run -n fourier pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt
  # Create project directory structure
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects
  # Setup test project (commit hash provided via --build-arg)
  ARG COMMIT_HASH
  RUN cd tool/scripts && \
      bash general_setup.sh /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects diana-hep/coax local "${COMMIT_HASH}"
  # Set default command
  WORKDIR /workspace
  CMD ["conda", "run", "--no-capture-output", "-n", "fourier", "bash"]
--- End of Iteration 1 ---

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:20.04
  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  # Install system dependencies including ca-certificates for SSL
  RUN apt-get update && \
      apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
      ca-certificates \
      git build-essential curl cmake swig \
      libeigen3-dev libc6-dev \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev libsdl-ttf2.0-dev libsdl1.2-dev \
      subversion ffmpeg libswscale-dev libavformat-dev libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev portaudio19-dev libsndfile1-dev pkg-config \
      libopenmpi-dev libsdl2-dev libsdl2-image-dev libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev libboost-all-dev mesa-utils xvfb x11vnc \
      libpq-dev gdal-bin libgdal-dev && \
      uname -m | grep x86_64 && \
      dpkg -l | grep -E 'libsdl|ffmpeg|portaudio|boost|gdal' && \
      rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Create conditional symlinks
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/locale.h ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/xlocale.h ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h || true
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/Eigen ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen || true
  # Install Miniconda with updated certificates
  RUN curl -O https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /root/miniconda && \
      ln -s /root/miniconda /root/anaconda3 && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  ENV PATH="/root/miniconda/bin:$PATH"
  # Create Conda environment
  RUN conda create -n fourier python=3.8 -y
  RUN conda install -n fourier -c conda-forge r-base r-essentials -y
  # Setup repository
  WORKDIR /workspace
  COPY . .
  # Install Python dependencies
  RUN conda run -n fourier pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt
  # Create project directory
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects
  # Setup test project
  ARG COMMIT_HASH
  RUN cd tool/scripts && \
      bash general_setup.sh /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects diana-hep/coax local "${COMMIT_HASH}"
  # Default command
  WORKDIR /workspace
  CMD ["conda", "run", "--no-capture-output", "-n", "fourier", "bash"]
--- End of Iteration 2 ---

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:20.04
  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  # Install system dependencies including ca-certificates for SSL
  RUN apt-get update && \
      apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
      ca-certificates \
      git build-essential curl cmake swig \
      libeigen3-dev libc6-dev \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev libsdl-ttf2.0-dev libsdl1.2-dev \
      subversion ffmpeg libswscale-dev libavformat-dev libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev portaudio19-dev libsndfile1-dev pkg-config \
      libopenmpi-dev libsdl2-dev libsdl2-image-dev libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev libboost-all-dev mesa-utils xvfb x11vnc \
      libpq-dev gdal-bin libgdal-dev && \
      uname -m | grep x86_64 && \
      dpkg -l | grep -E 'libsdl|ffmpeg|portaudio|boost|gdal' && \
      rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Create conditional symlinks
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/locale.h ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/xlocale.h ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h || true
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/Eigen ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen || true
  # Install Miniconda with updated certificates
  RUN curl -O https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /root/miniconda && \
      ln -s /root/miniconda /root/anaconda3 && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  ENV PATH="/root/miniconda/bin:$PATH"
  # Initialize Conda and create environment
  RUN /root/miniconda/bin/conda init bash && \
      . /root/.bashrc && \
      conda create -n fourier python=3.8 -y && \
      conda install -n fourier -c conda-forge r-base r-essentials -y
  # Setup repository
  WORKDIR /workspace
  COPY . .
  # Install Python dependencies
  RUN conda run -n fourier pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt
  # Create project directory
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects
  # Setup test project
  ARG COMMIT_HASH
  RUN cd tool/scripts && \
      bash general_setup.sh /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects diana-hep/coax local "${COMMIT_HASH}"
  # Default command
  WORKDIR /workspace
  CMD ["conda", "run", "--no-capture-output", "-n", "fourier", "bash"]
--- End of Iteration 3 ---

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:20.04
  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  # Install system dependencies including ca-certificates for SSL
  RUN apt-get update && \
      apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
      ca-certificates \
      git build-essential curl cmake swig \
      libeigen3-dev libc6-dev \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev libsdl-ttf2.0-dev libsdl1.2-dev \
      subversion ffmpeg libswscale-dev libavformat-dev libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev portaudio19-dev libsndfile1-dev pkg-config \
      libopenmpi-dev libsdl2-dev libsdl2-image-dev libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev libboost-all-dev mesa-utils xvfb x11vnc \
      libpq-dev gdal-bin libgdal-dev && \
      uname -m | grep x86_64 && \
      dpkg -l | grep -E 'libsdl|ffmpeg|portaudio|boost|gdal' && \
      rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Create conditional symlinks
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/locale.h ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/xlocale.h ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h || true
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/Eigen ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen || true
  # Install Miniconda with updated certificates
  RUN curl -O https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /root/miniconda && \
      ln -s /root/miniconda /root/anaconda3 && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  ENV PATH="/root/miniconda/bin:$PATH"
  # Update Conda and create environment with conda-forge priority
  RUN conda update -n base conda -y && \
      conda create -n fourier -c conda-forge python=3.8 r-base r-essentials -y
  # Setup repository
  WORKDIR /workspace
  COPY . .
  # Install Python dependencies
  RUN conda run -n fourier pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt
  # Create project directory
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects
  # Setup test project
  ARG COMMIT_HASH
  RUN cd tool/scripts && \
      bash general_setup.sh /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects diana-hep/coax local "${COMMIT_HASH}"
  # Default command
  WORKDIR /workspace
  CMD ["conda", "run", "--no-capture-output", "-n", "fourier", "bash"]
--- End of Iteration 5 ---

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:20.04
  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  # Install system dependencies including ca-certificates for SSL
  RUN apt-get update && \
      apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
      ca-certificates \
      git build-essential curl cmake swig \
      libeigen3-dev libc6-dev \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev libsdl-ttf2.0-dev libsdl1.2-dev \
      subversion ffmpeg libswscale-dev libavformat-dev libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev portaudio19-dev libsndfile1-dev pkg-config \
      libopenmpi-dev libsdl2-dev libsdl2-image-dev libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev libboost-all-dev mesa-utils xvfb x11vnc \
      libpq-dev gdal-bin libgdal-dev && \
      uname -m | grep x86_64 && \
      dpkg -l | grep -E 'libsdl|ffmpeg|portaudio|boost|gdal' && \
      rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Create conditional symlinks
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/locale.h ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/xlocale.h ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h || true
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/Eigen ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen || true
  # Install Miniconda with updated certificates
  RUN curl -O https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /root/miniconda && \
      ln -s /root/miniconda /root/anaconda3 && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  ENV PATH="/root/miniconda/bin:$PATH"
  # Create environment (removed failing conda update step)
  RUN conda create -n fourier -c conda-forge python=3.8 r-base r-essentials -y
  RUN conda env list | grep fourier
  # Setup repository
  WORKDIR /workspace
  COPY . .
  # Install Python dependencies
  RUN conda run -n fourier pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt
  # Create project directory
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects
  # Setup test project
  ARG COMMIT_HASH
  RUN cd tool/scripts && \
      bash general_setup.sh /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects diana-hep/coax local "${COMMIT_HASH}"
  # Default command
  WORKDIR /workspace
  CMD ["conda", "run", "--no-capture-output", "-n", "fourier", "bash"]

  ```
  # Create environment
  RUN conda create -n fourier -c conda-forge python=3.8 -y
  # Install R dependencies
  RUN conda install -n fourier -c conda-forge r-base r-essentials -y
  # Verify environment
  RUN conda env list | grep fourier
  ```

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:20.04
  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  # Install system dependencies including ca-certificates for SSL
  RUN apt-get update && \
      apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
      ca-certificates \
      git build-essential curl cmake swig \
      libeigen3-dev libc6-dev \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev libsdl-ttf2.0-dev libsdl1.2-dev \
      subversion ffmpeg libswscale-dev libavformat-dev libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev portaudio19-dev libsndfile1-dev pkg-config \
      libopenmpi-dev libsdl2-dev libsdl2-image-dev libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev libboost-all-dev mesa-utils xvfb x11vnc \
      libpq-dev gdal-bin libgdal-dev && \
      uname -m | grep x86_64 && \
      dpkg -l | grep -E 'libsdl|ffmpeg|portaudio|boost|gdal' && \
      rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Create conditional symlinks
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/locale.h ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/xlocale.h ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h || true
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/Eigen ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen || true
  # Install Miniconda and set up conda environment
  RUN curl -O https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /root/miniconda && \
      ln -s /root/miniconda /root/anaconda3 && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      . /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda create -n fourier -c conda-forge python=3.8 -y && \
      conda install -n fourier -c conda-forge r-base r-essentials -y && \
      conda env list | grep fourier
  # Set the PATH so that subsequent commands can find conda and other executables
  ENV PATH="/root/miniconda/bin:$PATH"
  # Setup repository
  WORKDIR /workspace
  COPY . .
  # Install Python dependencies
  RUN conda run -n fourier pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt
  # Create project directory
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects
  # Setup test project
  ARG COMMIT_HASH
  RUN cd tool/scripts && \
      bash general_setup.sh /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects diana-hep/coax local "${COMMIT_HASH}"
  # Default command
  WORKDIR /workspace
  CMD ["conda", "run", "--no-capture-output", "-n", "fourier", "bash"]

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:20.04
  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  # Install system dependencies including ca-certificates for SSL
  RUN apt-get update && \
      apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
      ca-certificates \
      git build-essential curl cmake swig \
      libeigen3-dev libc6-dev \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev libsdl-ttf2.0-dev libsdl1.2-dev \
      subversion ffmpeg libswscale-dev libavformat-dev libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev portaudio19-dev libsndfile1-dev pkg-config \
      libopenmpi-dev libsdl2-dev libsdl2-image-dev libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev libboost-all-dev mesa-utils xvfb x11vnc \
      libpq-dev gdal-bin libgdal-dev && \
      uname -m | grep x86_64 && \
      dpkg -l | grep -E 'libsdl|ffmpeg|portaudio|boost|gdal' && \
      rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Create conditional symlinks
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/locale.h ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/xlocale.h ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h || true
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/Eigen ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen || true
  # Install Miniconda
  RUN curl -O https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /root/miniconda && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  # Create symlink and set PATH
  RUN ln -s /root/miniconda /root/anaconda3
  ENV PATH="/root/miniconda/bin:$PATH"
  # Create environment
  RUN conda create -n fourier -c conda-forge python=3.8 -y
  # Install R dependencies
  RUN conda install -n fourier -c conda-forge r-base r-essentials -y
  # Verify environment
  RUN conda env list | grep fourier
  # Setup repository
  WORKDIR /workspace
  COPY . .
  # Install Python dependencies
  RUN conda run -n fourier pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt
  # Create project directory
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects
  # Setup test project
  ARG COMMIT_HASH
  RUN cd tool/scripts && \
      bash general_setup.sh /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects diana-hep/coax local "${COMMIT_HASH}"
  # Default command
  WORKDIR /workspace
  CMD ["conda", "run", "--no-capture-output", "-n", "fourier", "bash"]
--- End of Iteration 10 ---

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:20.04
  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  # Install system dependencies including ca-certificates for SSL
  RUN apt-get update && \
      apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
      ca-certificates \
      git build-essential curl cmake swig \
      libeigen3-dev libc6-dev \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev libsdl-ttf2.0-dev libsdl1.2-dev \
      subversion ffmpeg libswscale-dev libavformat-dev libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev portaudio19-dev libsndfile1-dev pkg-config \
      libopenmpi-dev libsdl2-dev libsdl2-image-dev libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev libboost-all-dev mesa-utils xvfb x11vnc \
      libpq-dev gdal-bin libgdal-dev && \
      uname -m | grep x86_64 && \
      dpkg -l | grep -E 'libsdl|ffmpeg|portaudio|boost|gdal' && \
      rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Create conditional symlinks
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/locale.h ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/xlocale.h ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h || true
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/Eigen ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen || true
  # Install Miniconda
  RUN curl -O https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /root/miniconda && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  # Create symlink and set PATH
  RUN ln -s /root/miniconda /root/anaconda3
  ENV PATH="/root/miniconda/bin:$PATH"
  # Verify conda and create environment
  RUN /root/miniconda/bin/conda --version && \
      /root/miniconda/bin/conda create -n fourier -c conda-forge python=3.8 -y
  # Install R dependencies
  RUN /root/miniconda/bin/conda install -n fourier -c conda-forge r-base r-essentials -y
  # Verify environment
  RUN /root/miniconda/bin/conda env list | grep fourier
  # Setup repository
  WORKDIR /workspace
  COPY . .
  # Install Python dependencies
  RUN /root/miniconda/bin/conda run -n fourier pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt
  # Create project directory
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects
  # Setup test project
  ARG COMMIT_HASH
  RUN cd tool/scripts && \
      bash general_setup.sh /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects diana-hep/coax local "${COMMIT_HASH}"
  # Default command
  WORKDIR /workspace
  CMD ["/root/miniconda/bin/conda", "run", "--no-capture-output", "-n", "fourier", "bash"]
--- End of Iteration 12 ---

  RUN apt-get update && \
      apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \

      git build-essential curl cmake swig \
      libeigen3-dev libc6-dev \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev libsdl-ttf2.0-dev libsdl1.2-dev \
      subversion ffmpeg libswscale-dev libavformat-dev libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev portaudio19-dev libsndfile1-dev pkg-config \
      libopenmpi-dev libsdl2-dev libsdl2-image-dev libsdl2-ttf-dev \

      dpkg -l | grep -E 'libsdl|ffmpeg|portaudio|boost|gdal' && \
      rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*

  RUN [ -e /usr/include/locale.h ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/xlocale.h ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h || true
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/Eigen ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen || true
  # Install Miniconda
  RUN curl -O https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /root/miniconda && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  # Create symlink and set PATH
  RUN ln -s /root/miniconda /root/anaconda3
  ENV PATH="/root/miniconda/bin:$PATH"
  # Initialize conda and create environment
  RUN . /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda --version && \
      conda create -n fourier -c conda-forge python=3.8 -y
  # Install R dependencies
  RUN . /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda install -n fourier -c conda-forge r-base r-essentials -y
  # Verify environment
  RUN . /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda env list | grep fourier
  # Setup repository
  WORKDIR /workspace
  COPY . .
  # Install Python dependencies
  RUN /root/miniconda/bin/conda run -n fourier pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt
  # Create project directory

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:20.04
  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  # Install system dependencies including ca-certificates for SSL
  RUN apt-get update && \
      apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
      ca-certificates \
      git build-essential curl cmake swig \
      libeigen3-dev libc6-dev \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev libsdl-ttf2.0-dev libsdl1.2-dev \
      subversion ffmpeg libswscale-dev libavformat-dev libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev portaudio19-dev libsndfile1-dev pkg-config \
      libopenmpi-dev libsdl2-dev libsdl2-image-dev libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev libboost-all-dev mesa-utils xvfb x11vnc \
      libpq-dev gdal-bin libgdal-dev && \
      uname -m | grep x86_64 && \
      dpkg -l | grep -E 'libsdl|ffmpeg|portaudio|boost|gdal' && \
      rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Create conditional symlinks
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/locale.h ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/xlocale.h ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h || true
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/Eigen ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen || true
  # Install Miniconda
  RUN curl -O https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /root/miniconda && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  # Create symlink and set PATH
  RUN ln -s /root/miniconda /root/anaconda3
  ENV PATH="/root/miniconda/bin:$PATH"
  # Initialize conda and create environment using absolute paths
  RUN /root/miniconda/bin/conda --version && \
      /root/miniconda/bin/conda create -n fourier -c conda-forge python=3.8 -y
  # Install R dependencies using absolute paths
  RUN /root/miniconda/bin/conda install -n fourier -c conda-forge r-base r-essentials -y
  # Verify environment using absolute path
  RUN /root/miniconda/bin/conda env list | grep fourier
  # Setup repository
  WORKDIR /workspace
  COPY . .
  # Install Python dependencies
  RUN /root/miniconda/bin/conda run -n fourier pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt
  # Create project directory
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects
  # Setup test project
  ARG COMMIT_HASH
  RUN cd tool/scripts && \
      bash general_setup.sh /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects diana-hep/coax local "${COMMIT_HASH}"
  # Default command
  WORKDIR /workspace
  CMD ["/root/miniconda/bin/conda", "run", "--no-capture-output", "-n", "fourier", "bash"]

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:20.04
  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  # Install system dependencies including ca-certificates for SSL
  RUN apt-get update && \
      apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
      ca-certificates \
      git build-essential curl cmake swig \
      libeigen3-dev libc6-dev \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev libsdl-ttf2.0-dev libsdl1.2-dev \
      subversion ffmpeg libswscale-dev libavformat-dev libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev portaudio19-dev libsndfile1-dev pkg-config \
      libopenmpi-dev libsdl2-dev libsdl2-image-dev libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev libboost-all-dev mesa-utils xvfb x11vnc \
      libpq-dev gdal-bin libgdal-dev && \
      uname -m | grep x86_64 && \
      dpkg -l | grep -E 'libsdl|ffmpeg|portaudio|boost|gdal' && \
      rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Create conditional symlinks
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/locale.h ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/xlocale.h ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h || true
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/Eigen ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen || true
  # Install Miniconda
  RUN curl -O https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /root/miniconda && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  # Create symlink and set PATH
  RUN ln -s /root/miniconda /root/anaconda3
  ENV PATH="/root/miniconda/bin:$PATH"
  # Verify conda initialization and version
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda --version"
  # Create environment with verbose output
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda create -n fourier -c conda-forge python=3.8 -y -v"
  # Install R dependencies
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda install -n fourier -c conda-forge r-base r-essentials -y"
  # Verify environment
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda env list | grep fourier"
  # Setup repository
  WORKDIR /workspace
  COPY . .
  # Install Python dependencies
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda run -n fourier pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt"
  # Create project directory
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects
  # Setup test project
  ARG COMMIT_HASH
  RUN cd tool/scripts && \
      bash general_setup.sh /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects diana-hep/coax local "${COMMIT_HASH}"
  # Default command
  WORKDIR /workspace
  CMD ["/root/miniconda/bin/conda", "run", "--no-capture-output", "-n", "fourier", "bash"]
--- End of Iteration 16 ---

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:20.04
  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  # Install system dependencies including ca-certificates for SSL
  RUN apt-get update && \
      apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
      ca-certificates \
      git build-essential curl cmake swig \
      libeigen3-dev libc6-dev \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev libsdl-ttf2.0-dev libsdl1.2-dev \
      subversion ffmpeg libswscale-dev libavformat-dev libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev portaudio19-dev libsndfile1-dev pkg-config \
      libopenmpi-dev libsdl2-dev libsdl2-image-dev libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev libboost-all-dev mesa-utils xvfb x11vnc \
      libpq-dev gdal-bin libgdal-dev && \
      uname -m | grep x86_64 && \
      dpkg -l | grep -E 'libsdl|ffmpeg|portaudio|boost|gdal' && \
      rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Create conditional symlinks
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/locale.h ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/xlocale.h ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h || true
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/Eigen ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen || true
  # Install Miniconda
  RUN curl -O https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /root/miniconda && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  # Create symlink and set PATH
  RUN ln -s /root/miniconda /root/anaconda3
  ENV PATH="/root/miniconda/bin:$PATH"
  # Verify conda initialization and version
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda --version"
  # Create environment with channel priority settings
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda create -n fourier -c conda-forge --override-channels --strict-channel-priority python=3.8 -y"
  # Install R dependencies
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda install -n fourier -c conda-forge r-base r-essentials -y"
  # Verify environment
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda env list | grep fourier"
  # Setup repository
  WORKDIR /workspace
  COPY . .
  # Install Python dependencies
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda run -n fourier pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt"
  # Create project directory
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects
  # Setup test project
  ARG COMMIT_HASH
  RUN cd tool/scripts && \
      bash general_setup.sh /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects diana-hep/coax local "${COMMIT_HASH}"
  # Default command
  WORKDIR /workspace
  CMD ["/root/miniconda/bin/conda", "run", "--no-capture-output", "-n", "fourier", "bash"]
--- End of Iteration 17 ---

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:20.04
  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  # Update package lists
  RUN apt-get update
  # Install system dependencies
  RUN apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
      ca-certificates \
      git build-essential curl cmake swig \
      libeigen3-dev libc6-dev \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev libsdl-ttf2.0-dev libsdl1.2-dev \
      subversion ffmpeg libswscale-dev libavformat-dev libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev portaudio19-dev libsndfile1-dev pkg-config \
      libopenmpi-dev libsdl2-dev libsdl2-image-dev libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev libboost-all-dev mesa-utils xvfb x11vnc \
      libpq-dev gdal-bin libgdal-dev
  # Log architecture information
  RUN uname -m && echo "Architecture: $(uname -m)"
  # Verify installed packages
  RUN dpkg -l | (grep -E 'libsdl|ffmpeg|portaudio|boost|gdal' || echo "No matching packages found")
  # Clean up apt cache
  RUN rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Create conditional symlinks
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/locale.h ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/xlocale.h ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h || true
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/Eigen ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen || true
  # Install Miniconda
  RUN curl -O https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /root/miniconda && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  # Create symlink and set PATH
  RUN ln -s /root/miniconda /root/anaconda3
  ENV PATH="/root/miniconda/bin:$PATH"
  # Verify conda
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda --version"
  # Create environment
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda create -n fourier -c conda-forge --override-channels --strict-channel-priority python=3.8 -y"
  # Install R dependencies
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda install -n fourier -c conda-forge r-base r-essentials -y"
  # Verify environment
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda env list | grep fourier"
  # Setup repository
  WORKDIR /workspace
  COPY . .
  # Install Python dependencies
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda run -n fourier pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt"
  # Create project directory
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects
  # Setup test project
  ARG COMMIT_HASH
  RUN cd tool/scripts && \
      bash general_setup.sh /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects diana-hep/coax local "${COMMIT_HASH}"
  # Default command
  WORKDIR /workspace
  CMD ["/root/miniconda/bin/conda", "run", "--no-capture-output", "-n", "fourier", "bash"]

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:20.04
  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  # Update package lists
  RUN apt-get update
  # Install system dependencies
  RUN apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
      ca-certificates \
      git build-essential curl cmake swig \
      libeigen3-dev libc6-dev \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev libsdl-ttf2.0-dev libsdl1.2-dev \
      subversion ffmpeg libswscale-dev libavformat-dev libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev portaudio19-dev libsndfile1-dev pkg-config \
      libopenmpi-dev libsdl2-dev libsdl2-image-dev libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev libboost-all-dev mesa-utils xvfb x11vnc \
      libpq-dev gdal-bin libgdal-dev
  # Log architecture information
  RUN uname -m && echo "Architecture: $(uname -m)"
  # Verify installed packages
  RUN dpkg -l | (grep -E 'libsdl|ffmpeg|portaudio|boost|gdal' || echo "No matching packages found")
  # Clean up apt cache
  RUN rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Create conditional symlinks
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/locale.h ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/xlocale.h ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h || true
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/Eigen ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen || true
  # Install Miniconda
  RUN curl -O https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /root/miniconda && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  # Create symlink and set PATH
  RUN ln -s /root/miniconda /root/anaconda3
  ENV PATH="/root/miniconda/bin:$PATH"
  # Verify conda
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda --version"
  # Update conda before environment creation
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda update -n base -c defaults conda -y"
  # Create environment
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda create -n fourier -c conda-forge --override-channels --strict-channel-priority python=3.8 -y"
  # Install R dependencies
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda install -n fourier -c conda-forge r-base r-essentials -y"
  # Verify environment
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda env list | grep fourier"
  # Setup repository
  WORKDIR /workspace
  COPY . .
  # Install Python dependencies
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda run -n fourier pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt"
  # Create project directory
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects
  # Setup test project
  ARG COMMIT_HASH
  RUN cd tool/scripts && \
      bash general_setup.sh /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects diana-hep/coax local "${COMMIT_HASH}"
  # Default command
  WORKDIR /workspace
  CMD ["/root/miniconda/bin/conda", "run", "--no-capture-output", "-n", "fourier", "bash"]

DOCKERFILE:
  FROM ubuntu:20.04
  ENV DEBIAN_FRONTEND=noninteractive
  # Update package lists
  RUN apt-get update
  # Install system dependencies
  RUN apt-get install -y --no-install-recommends \
      ca-certificates \
      git build-essential curl cmake swig \
      libeigen3-dev libc6-dev \
      libsdl-image1.2-dev libsdl-ttf2.0-dev libsdl1.2-dev \
      subversion ffmpeg libswscale-dev libavformat-dev libavcodec-dev \
      libfreetype6-dev portaudio19-dev libsndfile1-dev pkg-config \
      libopenmpi-dev libsdl2-dev libsdl2-image-dev libsdl2-ttf-dev \
      libsdl2-gfx-dev libboost-all-dev mesa-utils xvfb x11vnc \
      libpq-dev gdal-bin libgdal-dev
  # Log architecture information
  RUN uname -m && echo "Architecture: $(uname -m)"
  # Verify installed packages
  RUN dpkg -l | (grep -E 'libsdl|ffmpeg|portaudio|boost|gdal' || echo "No matching packages found")
  # Clean up apt cache
  RUN rm -rf /var/lib/apt/lists/*
  # Create conditional symlinks
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/locale.h ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/xlocale.h ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/locale.h /usr/include/xlocale.h || true
  RUN [ -e /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen ] && [ ! -e /usr/include/Eigen ] && \
      ln -s /usr/include/eigen3/Eigen /usr/include/Eigen || true
  # Install Miniconda
  RUN curl -O https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh && \
      bash Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -b -p /root/miniconda && \
      rm Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh
  # Create symlink and set PATH
  RUN ln -s /root/miniconda /root/anaconda3
  ENV PATH="/root/miniconda/bin:$PATH"
  # Verify conda
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda --version"
  # Create environment
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && conda create -n fourier -c conda-forge --override-channels --strict-channel-priority python=3.8 -y"
  # Install R dependencies
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda install -n fourier -c conda-forge r-base r-essentials -y"
  # Verify environment
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda env list | grep fourier"
  # Setup repository
  WORKDIR /workspace
  COPY . .
  # Install Python dependencies
  RUN bash -c "source /root/miniconda/etc/profile.d/conda.sh && \
      conda run -n fourier pip install --no-cache-dir -r requirements.txt"
  # Create project directory
  RUN mkdir -p /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects
  # Setup test project
  ARG COMMIT_HASH
  RUN cd tool/scripts && \
      bash general_setup.sh /home/cc/EnvGym/data/flex/projects diana-hep/coax local "${COMMIT_HASH}"
  # Default command
  WORKDIR /workspace
  CMD ["/root/miniconda/bin/conda", "run", "--no-capture-output", "-n", "fourier", "bash"]
